TELEKINESIS: Move objects with psionic force

Syntax: telekinesis [at <target>]
        psi telekinesis [at <target>]

DESCRIPTION:
  Move objects without touching them. Costs 2 ISP (2 ISP per 10 lbs in
  sustained use). Range: same room.

  Examples:
    telekinesis at crate
    psi telekinesis at door

NOTES:
  You must know telekinesis and have enough ISP.
  In combat, using psionics costs one attack from your APM pool.

SEE ALSO: psi, psionics
